hat%20man%20on-screen%20there%20(Kohli)%20might%20have%20a%20few%20questions%20to%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20Ponting%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKohli%20and%20Konstas%20come%20together%20and%20make%20contact%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAUSvIND%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AUSvIND%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fadb09clEqd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fadb09clEqd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%207Cricket%20(%407Cricket)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F7Cricket%2Fstatus%2F1872075722249912813%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20former%20England%20captain%20Michael%20Vaughan%20echoed%20Ponting's%20sentiments%2C%20saying%20the%20match%20referee%20is%20expected%20to%20seriously%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20act%20against%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20umpires%20and%20the%20referee%20will%20have%20a%20good%20look%20at%20that.%20Fielders%20should%20be%20nowhere%20near%20the%20batsman%20at%20that%20stage.%20Every%20fieldsman%20on%20the%20ground%20knows%20where%20the%20batsmen%20will%20congregate%20and%20get%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looked%20to%20me%20that%20Konstas%20looked%20up%20really%20late%2C%20and%20wouldn't%20even%20know%20anyone%20was%20in%20front%20of%20him.%20That%20man%20on-screen%20there%20(Kohli)%20might%20have%20a%20few%20questions%20to%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20Ponting%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20he%20would%2C%26quot%3B%20Vaughan%20said%20when%20asked%20whether%20the%20match%20referee%2C%20Andy%20Pycroft%2C%20would%20look%20into%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20ICC%20Rulebook%20Says%20On%20The%20Incident%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20under%20Law%202.12%3A%20Inappropriate%20physical%20contact%20with%20a%20Player%2C%20Player%20Support%20Personnel%2C%20Umpire%2C%20Match%20Referee%2C%20or%20any%20other%20person%20(including%20a%20spectator)%20during%20an%20International%20Match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20further%20says%3A%20%26quot%3B%20Note%3A%20Any%20form%20of%20inappropriate%20physical%20contact%20is%20prohibited%20in%20cricket.%20Without%20limitation%2C%20Players%20will%20breach%20this%20regulation%20if%20they%20deliberately%2C%20recklessly%20and%2For%20negligently%20walk%20or%20run%20into%20or%20shoulder%20another%20Player%20or%20Umpire.%20When%20assessing%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20breach%2C%20the%20following%20factors%20(without%20limitation)%20shall%20be%20taken%20into%20account%3A%20(i)%20the%20context%20of%20the%20particular%20situation%2C%20including%2C%20without%20limitation%2C%20whether%20the%20contact%20was%20deliberate%20(i.e.%20intentional)%2C%20reckless%2C%20negligent%2C%20and%2For%20avoidable%3B%20(ii)%20the%20force%20of%20the%20contact%3B%20(iii)%20any%20resulting%20injury%20to%20the%20person%20with%20whom%20contact%20was%20made%3B%20and%20(iv)%20the%20person%20with%20whom%20contact%20was%20made.%20Level%201%20(Level%201%20is%20available%20only%20in%20the%20case%20of%20contact%20with%20Players%2C%20Player%20Support%20...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20ICC%20match%20referee%20Andy%20Pycroft.%20If%20Pycroft%20feels%20it%20was%20a%20Level%202%20offence%2C%20Kohli%20could%20be%20handed%203-4%20demerit%20points.%20Such%20a%20case%20could%20see%20Kohli%20being%20suspended%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20next%20match.%20If%20only%20a%20Level%201%20offense%20is%20considered%2C%20Kohli%20could%20escape%20with%20just%20a%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735187220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fpq523978_virat-kohli-and-sam-konstas-x_625x300_26_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22