ived%20a%20suspended%20sentence%20owing%20to%20her%20cooperation%20and%20commitment%20to%20rehabilitation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fglam-dealer-after-luigi-mangione-30-year-old-female-drug-dealers-mugshot-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F116667619.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fglam-dealer-after-luigi-mangione-30-year-old-female-drug-dealers-mugshot-goes-viral%2Famp_articleshow%2F116667619.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fglam-dealer-after-luigi-mangione-30-year-old-female-drug-dealers-mugshot-goes-viral%2Famp_articleshow%2F116667619.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20Airlines%20hit%20by%20cyberattack%3B%20domestic%2C%20international%20flights%20delayed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735184953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-airlines-jal-cyberattack-malfunction-flights-delayed-status-tokyo-124122600101_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Japan%20Airlines%20has%20apologised%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20passengers%20and%20assured%20that%20updates%20would%20follow%20as%20the%20situation%20evolves%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'SpaDeX'%20Mission%3A%20How%20ISRO%20Will%20Dock%20Two%20Satellites%20In%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20is%20attempting%20to%20mate%20two%20satellites%20in%20the%20near%20vacuum%20of%20space%2C%20both%20of%20which%20would%20travel%20at%20a%20velocity%20ten%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20a%20bullet%20-%20a%20tough%20challenge%20to%20arrest%20two%20orbiting%20space%20assets%20and%20nudge%20them%20into%20a%20single%20spacecraft.%20It%20will%20take%20place%20under%20the%20'SpaDeX'%20or%20Space%20Docking%20Experiment%20mission%20scheduled%20on%20December%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mission%20is%20called%20'space%20docking'%20and%20has%20been%20in%20the%20making%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20only%20Russia%2C%20US%2C%20and%20China%20have%20mastered%20the%20complex%20technology%20and%20none%20share%20the%20intricacies%20of%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20ISRO%20will%20dock%20two%20satellites%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PSLV%20rocket%20will%20carry%20two%20specially%20designed%20satellites%20each%20weighing%20about%20220%20kg%20and%20then%20attempt%20docking%20and%20undocking%20at%20470%20kilometers%20above%20the%20Earth.%20The%20space%20agency%20will%20use%20a%20specially%20designed%20space%20docking%20mechanism%20called%20the%20'Bhartiya%20Docking%20System'%20which%20meets%20the%20International%20Docking%20System%20Standard%20(IDSS)%20developed%20by%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20had%20to%20develop%20its%20own%20docking%20mechanism%20since%20no%20one%20shares%20the%20fine%20details%20of%20this%20hugely%20complex%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20Chairman%20Dr%20S%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20ISRO%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20patent%20on%20the%20Indian%20docking%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20satellites%20will%20be%20travelling%20at%20a%20velocity%20of%20about%2028%2C800%20kilometers%20per%20hour%20or%20about%2036%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20a%20commercial%20airplane%20or%20ten%20times%20the%20velocity%20of%20a%20bullet%20in%20the%20near-Earth%20orbit.%20Using%20specially%20designed%20rockets%20and%20a%20suite%20of%20sensors%20the%20relative%20velocities%20of%20the%20satellites%20will%20be%20slowed%20down%20to%20almost%20zero%20or%20just%20about%200.036%20kilometers%20per%20hour%20or%20to%2010%20millimeters%20per%20second%20and%20then%20they%20will%20be%20mated%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20independent%20spacecraft%2C%20'Chaser'%20and%20'Target'%2C%20will%20be%20conjoined%20to%20become%20one%20entity%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fkmsjmddg_isro_625x300_26_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sounds%20simple%20but%20to%20do%20this%20autonomously%20is%20a%20Herculean%20challenge%20as%20the%20physics%20involved%20is%20complex%20since%20both%20satellites%20have%20to%20remain%20in%20orbit%20and%20more%20importantly%20not%20crash%20into%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMastering%20docking%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20if%20India%20has%20to%20send%20Chandryaan-4%2C%20build%20a%20space%20station%2C%20and%20then%20send%20an%20Indian%20to%20the%20moon...SpaDeX%20is%20one%20mission%20with%20many-many%20objectives%2C%20truly%20the%20fullest%20use%20of%20tax%20payer%20money%20to%20innovate%20and%20catapult%20India%20into%20the%20next%20league%20of%20space%20fairing%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fn2314q6g_isro-2_625x300_26_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%2C%20SpaDeX%20mission%20is%20a%20cost-effective%20technology%20demonstrator%20mission%20for%20the%20demonstration%20of%20in-space%20docking%20using%20two%20small%20spacecraft%20launched%20by%20PSLV.%20This%20technology%20is%20essential%20for%20India's%20space%20ambitions%20such%20as%20Indian%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20sample%20return%20from%20the%20moon%2C%20and%20the%20building%20and%20operation%20of%20Bharatiya%20Antariksh%20Station%20(BAS)%2C%20among%20others.%20In-space%20docking%20technology%20is%20essential%20when%20multiple%20rocket%20launches%20are%20required%20to%20achieve%20common%20mission%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SpaDeX%20mission%20was%20conceived%20and%20designed%20by%20scientists%20at%20ISRO%20but%20the%20final%20assembly%2C%20integration%2C%20and%20testing%20of%20the%20satellite%20was%20done%20at%20Ananth%20Technologies%20-%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20space%20technology%20company%20started%20in%201992%20by%20an%20ex-ISRO%20employee%20turned%20entrepreneur%20Dr%20Subba%20Rao%20Pavuluri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20bold%20move%20to%20let%20a%20private%20company%20undertake%20this%20complex%20job%20but%20they%20came%20out%20with%20flying%20colors%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20M%20Sankaran%2C%20Director%2C%20UR%20Rao%20Satellite%20Center%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bhartiya%20Docking%20System%20is%20so%20sophisticated%20and%20more%20modern%20that%20in%20its%20current%20avatar%2C%20it%20uses%20only%20two%20motors%20compared%20to%20the%2024%20motors%20used%20in%20the%20IDSS.%20In%20its%20current%20format%2C%20it%20is%20only%20450%20millimeters%20in%20diameter%20but%20the%20final%20goal%20will%20be%20to%20develop%20an%20800%20millimeter-diameter%20docking%20port%20that%20will%20connect%20the%20Indian%20Gaganyaan%20Crew%20Module%20to%20the%20Bhartiya%20Antariksha%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20docking%20experiment%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20done%20by%20early%20in%20the%20New%20Year%2C%20Dr%20Sankaran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20mission%2C%20India%20is%20marching%20towards%20becoming%20the%20fourth%20country%20in%20the%20world%20to%20have%20space%20docking%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735184820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Flml54vv8_isro_625x300_26_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2