ople%20%E2%80%94%20discrimination%2C%20marginalisation%2C%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20basic%20rights%2C%20and%20most%20significantly%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20identity%20in%20a%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%2C%20like%20many%20others%20from%20the%20Banjara%20community%2C%20lived%20a%20life%20on%20the%20move%2C%20travelling%20and%20trading%20goods.%20His%20parents%20lived%20a%20nomadic%20existence%2C%20while%20Paras%E2%80%99s%20eight%20older%20siblings%20never%20even%20attended%20school%20due%20to%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20constant%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20and%20grandfather%20would%20sell%20salt%2C%20that%20used%20to%20be%20our%20trade.%20They%20also%20used%20to%20sell%20cattle%20to%20farmers%20who%20needed%20them%20for%20agriculture.%20At%20cattle%20fairs%20organised%20by%20the%20Government%2C%20they%20would%20buy%20and%20take%20the%20cattle%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20mainly%20to%20the%20southern%20regions.%20There%2C%20tribal%20farmers%20rely%20on%20cattle%20for%20farming%20instead%20of%20using%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paras%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20transportation%20methods%20improved%20and%20small%20markets%20began%20setting%20up%2C%20this%20line%20of%20business%20became%20obsolete%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20then%20had%20to%20look%20for%20other%20ways%20of%20earning.%20With%20few%20options%20available%2C%20they%20shifted%20to%20labour%20work%20and%20formed%20a%20small%20community%20of%20labourers%20where%20everyone%20would%20work%20together.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20they%20decided%20that%20they%20nee