mes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-airlines-hit-by-massive-cyberattack-flights-affected-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F116666693.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-airlines-hit-by-massive-cyberattack-flights-affected-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F116666693.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandan%20Taparia%20of%20MOFSL%20recommends%20buying%20these%20stocks%20on%20Dec%2026%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735177248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fchandan-taparia-of-mofsl-recommends-buying-these-stocks-on-dec-26-124122600056_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lupin%20stock%20has%20broken%20out%20of%20a%20triple%20bottom%20pattern%20on%20the%20daily%20chart.%20It%20has%20also%20crossed%20above%20its%20key%20moving%20average%20suggesting%20bullish%20sentiment%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Confronted%20By%20Shastri%20On%20Poor%20Form%2C%20Kohli%20Says%20%26quot%3BThese%20Pitches%20Are...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETalismanic%20India%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20admitted%20he%20hasn't%20been%20disciplined%20enough%20in%20his%20last%20few%20innings%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20series.%20After%20scoring%20an%20unbeaten%20century%20at%20Perth%2C%20Kohli%20has%20since%20made%207%2C%2011%20and%203%20in%20this%20series%20currently%20locked%20at%201-1.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20would%20have%20told%20us%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20one%20all%20heading%20into%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%2C%20we%20would%20have%20taken%20it%20with%20both%20hands.%20I%20agree%2C%20last%20two%20or%20three%20innings%20hasn't%20gone%20the%20way%20I%20wanted%20to.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20I%20haven't%20been%20disciplined%20enough%20to%20stick%20in%20there%20and%2C%20really%20grind%20it%20out.%20That's%20what%20the%20challenge%20that%20Test%20Cricket%20brings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kohli%20to%20former%20India%20head%20coach%20Ravi%20Shastri%20ahead%20of%20day%20one's%20play%20in%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%20pitches%20have%20become%20livelier%20in%20Australia%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20his%20previous%20trips%20to%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CObviously%2C%20these%20pitches%20are%20much%20more%20livelier%20than%20the%20last%20time%20that%20we%20played%20here.%20So%20there's%20a%20different%20approach%20that's%20required%2C%20but%20that's%20something%20that%20I've%20taken%20a%20lot%20of%20pride%20in%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20counter%20different%20conditions%20and%20step%20up%20when%20the%20team%20wants%20me%20to%20or%20needs%20me%20to.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20get%20stuck%20in%2C%20as%20I%20said%2C%20go%20in%20there%2C%20get%20your%20eyes%20set%20in%2C%20play%20enough%20number%20of%20balls%20that%20you%20start%20playing%20your%20game%20afterwards%2C%20but%20respect%20the%20conditions%20foremost%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Virat%20Kohli%20interview%20at%20the%20MCG%20with%20Ravi%20Shastri.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3jU6dBSL9e%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F3jU6dBSL9e%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mufaddal%20Vohra%20(%40mufaddal_vohra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmufaddal_vohra%2Fstatus%2F1872068403789496719%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20how%20he%20deals%20with%20expectations%20of%20doing%20well%20in%20every%20outing%2C%20Kohli%20elaborated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWell%2C%20expectations%20are%20always%20going%20to%20be%20there%2C%20I%20guess%2C%20playing%20for%20your%20country%20firstly%20and%20then%20having%20performed%20for%20that%20long%20a%20period%2C%20the%20expectations%20are%20always%20going%20to%20follow.%20I%20think%20what's%20important%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20understand%20your%20own%20plans%20and%20you%20understand%20the%20space%20you%20are%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20start%20focusing%20on%20the%20expectations%2C%20then%20you%20drift%20away%20from%20what%20you%20need%20to%20do.%20So%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20just%20to%20follow%20the%20game%20plan%20that%20I%20have.%20Just%20stay%20very%20disciplined%20in%20my%20approach%2C%20and%20understand%20the%20situation%20of%20the%20game.%20That's%20something%20that's%20brought%20me%20success%20over%20so%20many%20years%20and%20really%20focus%20on%20what%20the%20team%20needs%20from%20me%20out%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20walk%20in%20early%2C%20then%20it's%20a%20different%20situation.%20If%20there's%20a%20partnership%2C%20then%20to%20capitalize%20and%20stretch%20that%20good%20period%20for%20the%20team.%20So%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20looking%20at%20situations%20and%20making%20sure%20you%20have%20your%20own%20game%20plan%20set.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20won%20Test%20matches%20in%20Melbourne%20in%202018%2F19%20and%202020%2F21%20respectively%2C%20and%20Kohli%20felt%20the%20series%20is%20well%20and%20truly%20on%20now.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20we%20played%20some%20really%20good%20cricket%20here.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20last%20time%20around%20when%20we%20played%2C%20we%20won.%20The%20year%20before%20that%2C%20we%20won%20as%20well.%20So%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20about%20understanding%20where%20the%20series%20is%20placed%2C%20and%20that%20takes%20away%20all%20the%20pressure%20on%20individuals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20it's%20all%20to%20play%20for.%20We%20are%201-all.%20We%20want%20to%20have%20a%20strong%20Test%20match%20here%2C%20try%20to%20go%20up%20in%20the%20series%20heading%20into%20SCG.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20cracker%20of%20a%20Test%20match.%20Both%20teams%20really%20want%20to%20win%20this%20one%2C%20and%20Australia%20is%20going%20to%20bring%20their%20A%20game%20and%20so%20are%20we.%20But%2C%20the%20opportunity%20is%20in%20front%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20avoid%20the%20follow%20on%20in%20Brisbane%20and%20the%20way%20the%20tail%20got%20stuck%20in%2C%20an%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20are%20not%20batting%20again%20under%20pressure%20was%20massive.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20it%20ended%20up%20to%20be%20a%20draw%20when%20the%20situation%20was%20looking%20bleak%20for%20us.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20really%20got%20stuck%20in%2C%20shown%20character%20at%20the%20right%20stage%2C%20and%20that%20has%20given%20us%20another%20chance%20to%20start%20afresh%20and%20approach%20this%20game%20like%20we%20approached%20the%20first%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli's%20record%20at%20the%20MCG%20has%20seen%20him%20amass%20316%20runs%20in%20three%20Tests%2C%20coming%20at%20an%20average%20of%2052.66.%20%E2%80%9CIt's%20a%20special%20place.%20I%20mean%2C%20right%20from%20my%20first%20tour%2C%20I%20understood%20the%20occasion%20that%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%20match%20brings%20and%20(brings)%20some%20good%20memories%20in%20these%20Test%20matches.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20tour%20that%20I%20played%20here%2C%20we%20won%20and%20went%20up%202-1%20in%20the%20series%2C%20so%20that%20was%20memorable.%20Then%20even%20in%202014-15%2C%20I%20got%20a%20Test%20hundred%20here.%20So%2C%20pretty%20fond%20memories%20of%20this%20ground%2C%20not%20just%20in%20Test%20cricket%20but%20other%20formats%20as%20well.%20It's%20a%20special%20place%20to%20come%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published