hra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20met%20here%20at%20BJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda's%20residence%20on%20Wednesday%20on%20the%20birth%20centenary%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20NDA%20leaders%20discussed%20the%20Congress'%20recent%20political%20attack%20on%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20and%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20speak%20in%20a%20united%20voice%20to%20counter%20the%20party's%20%26quot%3Bfake%20narrative%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20attacked%20Mr%20Shah%20alleging%20insult%20of%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20with%20the%20home%20minister%20accusing%20the%20opposition%20party%20of%20using%20a%20short%20clip%20of%20his%20speech%20to%20distort%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20and%20Mr%20Nadda%20said%20the%20ruling%20alliance's%20focus%20should%20remain%20on%20good%20governance%20and%20people's%20welfare%2C%20which%20have%20brought%20it%20support%20from%20the%20masses%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Mr%20Shah%20and%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20JD(U)%20leader%20and%20Union%20minister%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20Apna%20Dal%20(S)%20president%20and%20Union%20minister%20Anupriya%20Patel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20JD(S)%20leader%20and%20Union%20minister%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20were%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%20With%20the%20NDA%20putting%20in%20a%20broad%20mechanism%20to%20boost%20coordination%2C%20it%20was%20noted%20that%20its%20members%20would%20continue%20to%20consult%20over%20key%20issues%2C%20with%20ministers%20and%20other%20senior%20leaders%20meeting%20the%20MPs%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar's%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(S)%20leader%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20also%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Morcha%20(RLM)%20president%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20and%20Thushar%20Vellappally%2C%20president%20of%20Bharath%20Dharma%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20were%20also%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20was%20no%20official%20word%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20sources%20said%20good%20governance%20and%20political%20issues%20were%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGood%20governance%20was%20a%20key%20theme%20of%20the%20Vajpayee%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20decided%20to%20hold%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20alliance%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20BJP%20stalwart%2C%20who%20is%20credited%20with%20successfully%20running%20the%20first%20coalition%20government%20for%20its%20full%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAttended%20the%20NDA%20leaders'%20meeting%20in%20New%20Delhi%20today.%20Under%20the%20visionary%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20India%20is%20achieving%20unprecedented%20milestones%20and%20has%20positioned%20itself%20as%20a%20global%20superpower%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nadda%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NDA%20government%20remains%20steadfast%20in%20its%20pursuit%20of%20the%20vision%20of%20'Viksit%20Bharat%402047'%2C%20ensuring%20a%20brighter%20and%20more%20prosperous%20future%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh's%20NISHAD%20Party%20chief%20Sanjay%20Nishad%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Binformal%26quot%3B%20meeting%20of%20the%20NDA%20leaders%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20birth%20centenary%20of%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20future%20strategy%20is%20to%20move%20forward%20together.%20We%20have%20to%20show%20unity%20in%20all%20the%20upcoming%20elections...everyone%20congratulated%20(the%20BJP%20leaders)%20in%20the%20meeting%20for%20the%20victory%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishad%20said%20the%20meeting%20also%20discussed%20coalition%20strategy%20to%20ensure%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20work%26quot%3B%20done%20by%20P