it%20at%20a%20holding%20point.%20The%20pilot%20misinterpreted%20the%20instruction%2C%20believing%20it%20to%20be%20permission%20to%20enter%20the%20runway%20for%20takeoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20moments%20before%20the%20collision%2C%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20pilot%20ordered%20his%20co-pilot%20to%20go%20through%20a%20checklist%20that%20is%20typically%20performed%20once%20final%20takeoff%20clearance%20has%20been%20granted.%20The%20pilot%2C%20who%20survived%2C%20told%20investigators%20he%20thought%20he%20heard%20%26quot%3Bcleared%20for%20takeoff%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20control%20tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20that%20the%20pilot%20said%20he%20was%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20which%20could%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20misinterpretation.%20The%20Coast%20Guard%20plane%20was%20traveling%20to%20the%20city%20of%20Niigata%20to%20deliver%20emergency%20supplies%20after%20recent%20earthquakes%20on%20Japan's%20west%20coast%2C%20and%20the%20pilot%20said%20he%20was%20worried%20about%20his%20crew%20getting%20home%20late%20from%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20there%20were%20other%20contributing%20factors%20to%20the%20collision%3A%20Air%20traffic%20control%20failed%20to%20realize%20that%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20plane%20had%20entered%20the%20runway%2C%20despite%20the%20runway%20occupancy%20alert%2C%20and%20the%20JAL%20plane%20didn't%20see%20the%20other%20aircraft%20as%20it%20was%20descending%20due%20to%20limited%20visibility.%20The%20accident%20occurred%20around%205%3A47%20p.m.%2C%20after%20sunset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20of%20the%20six%20people%20aboard%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20aircraft%20died.%20The%20pilot%20survived%20but%20was%20seriously%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20379%20passengers%20and%20crew%20on%20the%20passenger%20plane%20escaped%20just%20before%20the%20jet%20erupted%20into%20flames.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-error-caused-tokyo