a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392141%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20sunset%20paints%20a%20silhouette%20of%20jeeps%20near%20Sandakphu%3B%20image%3A%20Sasang%20Gurung%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Phalut%20trek%20would%20take%20at%20least%20five%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sangay%20Sherpa%2C%20who%20manages%20the%20Singalila%20Jungle%20Lodge%20in%20Palmauja%20near%20Dhotrey.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20lodging%20throughout%20the%20entire%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Dhotrey%20is%20among%20numerous%20villages%20that%20trekkers%20choose%20to%20acclimatise%20before%20starting%20their%20Sandakphu%20journey.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESasang%20informs%20that%20the%20Singalila%20Ridge%20is%20dotted%20with%20such%20offbeat%20destinations.%20Since%20tourism%20is%20an%20important%20means%20of%20livelihood%2C%20there%20are%20a%20sizable%20number%20of%20homestays%20and%20lodges.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20best%20to%20make%20bookings%20in%20advance%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20holiday%20season%2C%20Sasang%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDoes%20it%20snow%20in%20Sandakphu%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes!%20The%20higher%20altitudes%20have%20traditionally%20been%20blessed%20with%20snowfall%20between%20the%20months%20of%20December%20and%20February.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20tad%20bit%20erratic%2C%20thanks%20to%20climate%20change.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20some%20light%20snowfall%20in%20September%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sasang.%20%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20it%20snowed%20in%20March.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20inform%20me%20that%20the%20best%20time%20to%20make%20the%20trek%20is%20between%20September%20and%20November%20when%20the%20skies%20are%20crystal%20clear%2C%20or%20March%20and%20April%20when%20the%20forests%20are%20lush.%