ed%20by%20play%20sessions%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20and%20a%20round-up%20on%20the%20daily%20news%20at%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20all%20the%20extra%20time%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20use%20it%20to%20find%20out%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20good%20at%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnavi%20says.%20For%20instance%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20an%20avid%20reader%20or%20writer.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20her%20curiosity%20was%20piqued%20when%20her%20mother%20assigned%20her%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302842%2Fchildren-book-recommendations-by-indian-authors-ruskin-bond-chitra-banerjee-anu-kumar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreative%20writing%3C%2Fa%3E%20passages%20one%20day.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20where%20I%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20writing.%20I%20used%20my%20time%20to%20watch%20relevant%20videos%2C%20develop%20a%20storyline%20for%20my%20books%2C%20and%20research%20the%20India%20of%20the%20past%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20life%2C%20the%20food%20habits%20and%20the%20accommodation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFzpm4jWhF1g%3Fsi%3DsXQ-DWwHgiyzyL0M%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20homeschooling%20make%20you%20introverted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20you%20aren%E2%80%99t%20expected%20to%20dress%20up%20and%20go%20to%20school%2C%20participate%20in%20school%20events%2C%20have%20annual%20days%20or%20sports%20days%20to%20channel%20your%20energies%20in%2C%20there%20is%20an%20understandable%20tendency%20to%20retreat%20into%20a%20shell.%20But%20this%20is%20where%2C%20Vaishnavi%20says%2C%20your%20hobbies%20will%20