enges%20faced%20by%20farmers%20in%20his%20home%20region%2C%20Aman%20took%20a%20significant%20leap.%20He%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20himself%20full-time%20to%20this%20cause%2C%20collaborating%20with%20local%20farmers%20in%20Unnao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20I%20saw%20businesses%20like%20Phool%2C%20a%20Kanpur-based%20brand%20that%20was%20just%20starting%20out%20at%20the%20time%2C%20doing%20great%20work.%20That%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20believe%20that%20if%20someone%20from%20my%20part%20of%20the%20world%20could%20create%20something%20like%20that%2C%20so%20could%20I%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecognising%20the%20peanut%20crisis%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20internship%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Aman%20had%20gained%20firsthand%20insights%20into%20the%20systemic%20issues%20plaguing%20the%20agricultural%20sector.%20In%20Unnao%2C%20he%20and%20Nutty%20Village%20co-founder%2C%20Sushant%20Berma%2C%20noticed%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20locally%20grown%20peanuts.%20This%20sparked%20their%20curiosity%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20peanut%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20while%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20eating%20peanuts%2C%20we%20started%20talking%20about%20their%20great%20quality.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20out%20and%20do%20some%20research%20to%20see%20what%20was%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sushant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20major%20challenge%20faced%20by%20Unnao%E2%80%99s%20groundnut%20farmers%20was%20the%20extremely%20low%20prices%20they%20received%20for%20their%20produce.%20These%20farmers%20were%20forced%20to%20sell%20their%20groundnuts%20for%20a%20mere%20Rs%2030%20to%20Rs%2040%20per%20kilogram%2C%20without%20any%20government%20support%20or%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20recognition%20in%20agricultural%20surveys%20lists%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20issue.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20these%20farmers%20were%20deprived%20of%20essential%20support%20programmes%2C%20hindering%20their%20ability%20to%20earn%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%E2%80%99s%20research%20unveiled%20a%20potential%20solution%3A%20empowering%20farmers%20to%20undertake%20primary%20processing%20themselves.%20By%20handling%20tasks%20like%20shelling%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20grading%2C%20farmers%20could%20significantly%20increase%20their%20earnings%20by%2050-60%25.%20To%20realise%20this%20vision%2C%20Aman%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20State%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%20(UPSRLM)%20seeking%20support%20for%20establishing%20a%20producer%20group%20dedicated%20to%20primary%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Aman%E2%80%99s%20proposal%2C%20the%20Government%20provided%20a%20grant%20that%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20set%20up%20facilities%20for%20shelling%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20grading%20groundnuts.%20This%20primary%20processing%20would%20enable%20farmers%20to%20retain%20a%20higher%20portion%20of%20the%20profits.%20By%20working%20collectively%2C%20the%20farmers%20could%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20produce%20and%20access%20better%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20fresh%20produce%20delivery%20service%20in%202020%20evolved%20into%20Nutty%20Village%20in%202022.%20With%20a%20vision%20to%20empower%20farmers%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20aims%20to%20help%20them%20establish%20their%20own%20processing%20units%2C%20directly%20sourcing%20high-quality%20produce%20at%20fair%20prices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20champion%20both%20the%20exceptional%20products%20these%20farmers%20create%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270093%2Fpeanut-jaggery-health-benefits-indian-food-recipe-for-chikki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant-based%20proteins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20through%20our%20peanut%20butters%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUplifting%20rural%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20farmers%20had%20set%20up%20their%20primary%20processing%20units%2C%20Aman%20started%20purchasing%20the%20processed%20groundnuts%20at%20Rs%20100-120%20per%20kilogram%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20quality%2C%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20prices%20they%20were%20getting.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20the%20primary%20processing%20is%20now%20done%20by%20these%20farmers%2C%20they%20also%20have%20their%20own%20seeds%20to%20put%20back%20into%20harvesting%20the%20crop%20for%20the%20next%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20met%20Aman%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20how%20we%20could%20all%20work%20together%20for%20better%20profits.%20He%20brought%20us%20seeds%20and%20we%20worked%20on%20figuring%20out%20the%20best%20farming%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish%20Singh%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Unnao.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20our%20soil%20tested.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20that%20was%20something%20you%E2%80%99re%20supposed%20to%20do.%20Checking%20and%20regulating%20the%20pH%20levels%2C%20nitrogen%20phosphate%2C%20and%20carbon%2016%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20any%20of%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20scientific%20perspective%2C%20Aman%20connected%20them%20with%20Dr%20Kishan%20Chandra%2C%20a%20scientist%20specialising%20in%20organic%20farming%2C%20waste%20management%2C%20and%20bio-fertiliser%20production.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20a%20decomposer%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20mixture%20with%20water%20and%20essential%20nutrients%20that%20helps%20kill%20pests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manish%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202920px)%20100vw%2C%202920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aman%20Kumar%20and%20his%20co-founder%20pose%20with%20farmers%20at%20their%20primary%20processing%20space.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515.jpeg%202920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-1200x900.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390896%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222190%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAman%20Kumar%20and%20his%20co-founder%20pose%20with%20farmers%20at%20their%20primary%20processing%20space%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20that%20solution%20in%20200%20liters%20of%20water.%20The%20results%20have%20been%20quite%20good.%20The%20yield%20has%20improved%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoil%20has%20become%20softer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20pH%20of%20our%20soil%2C%20which%20was%208.5%2C%20is%20now%20down%20to%207.5.%20We%E2%80%99re%20all%20working%20very%20hard%20to%20make%20it%20even%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20primary%20processing%20infrastructure%20was%20established%2C%20Aman%20envisioned%20a%20future%20beyond%20mere%20raw%20material%20supply.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20secondary%20processing%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20this%20enterprise%20to%20newer%20heights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20Recognising%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20clean%2C%20preservative-free%20peanut%20butter%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20developing%20his%20own%20unique%20product.%20After%20months%20of%20experimentation%2C%20he%20formulated%20a%20healthy%20peanut%20butter%20that%20would%20appeal%20to%20health-conscious%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20a%20grant%20from%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Government%20and%20a%20contribution%20of%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20from%20Anuj%20Sharma%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20TISS%2C%20Aman%20was%20able%20to%20purchase%20the%20necessary%20machinery%20and%20start%20producing%20peanut%20butter.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20promoting%20the%20local%20peanut%20variety%2C%20food%20security%2C%20and%20transparency%20in%20our%20ingredients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nutty%20Village%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20empowering%20rural%20communities%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20To%20further%20enhance%20women%E2%80%99s%20participation%2C%20they%20collaborated%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%20to%20form%20Self-Help%20Groups%20(SHGs).%20These%20SHGs%20provided%20women%20with%20access%20to%20peanut%20shelling%20machines%2C%20training%20them%20in%20the%20necessary%20skills%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20secondary%20processing%20of%20groundnuts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandkali%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20member%20of%20the%20self-help%20group%2C%20reflects%20on%20how%20her%20life%20has%20changed%20through%20their%20collective%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20I%20mostly%20worked%20at%20home.%20The%20societal%20structure%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20women%20to%20be%20out%20earning%2C%20and%20many%20like%20me%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20phone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20However%2C%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20Nutty%20Village%20and%20being%20involved%20in%20secondary%20processing%2C%20has%20empowered%20her%20in%20unexpected%20ways.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20Aman%20calls%20us%20for%20work%20with%20peanuts%2C%20we%20go%2C%20and%20we%20earn%20a%20good%20amount.%20The%20group%20I%20am%20in%20feels%20like%20a%20community%2C%20like%20a%20union.%20When%20we%20get%20work%2C%20we%20all%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20have%20to%20travel%20to%20nearby%20towns%20for%20higher%20wages%2C%20Chandkali%20is%20content%20to%20stay%20close%20to%20home.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20300%20rupees%20per%20day%20here.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20go%20far%20for%20work%2C%20being%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20able%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EConquering%20the%20hurdles%20to%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%20and%20his%20team%E2%80%99s%20journey%20was%20not%20without%20challenges.%20From%20persuading%20farmers%20to%20embrace%20new%20agricultural%20techniques%20to%20navigating%20complex%20bureaucratic%20processes%2C%20they%20encountered%20numerous%20obstacles.%20One%20significant%20hurdle%20was%20securing%20an%20electricity%20connection%20for%20their%20machinery%20unit%2C%20which%20involved%20navigating%20a%20labyrinth%20of%20bureaucratic%20red%20tape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20now%20have%20electricity%20connection%2C%20license%2C%20quality%20control%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20because%20I%20am%20CSIR%20incubated.%20I%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20connections%20back%20in%20college%20and%20when%20I%20was%20working%20for%20Fresh-ily%2C%20But%20the%20farmers%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%20for%20themselves.%20Even%20if%20they%20do%20want%20to%20start%20or%20scale%20their%20business%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20pay%20Rs%2060%2C000%20just%20to%20get%20an%20electricity%20connection.%20This%20needs%20to%20change%20at%20a%20policy%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20us%20too%2C%20we%20won%20a%20lot%20of%20grants%2C%20but%20it%20would%20take%20seven%20to%20eight%20months%20for%20the%20other%20installments%20to%20come%20in.%20As%20a%20founder%2C%20I%20can%20stretch%20out%20a%20few%20months%20but%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20expect%20my%20team%20of%20farmers%20to%20just%20wait%20for%20funding%20that%20was%20promised%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20stress%20of%20managing%20cash%20flow%20during%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20farmer%20harvests%20peanuts%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20carefully%20pulling%20the%20plants%20to%20collect%20the%20fresh%20crop%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-600x800.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-450x600.jpeg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-300x400.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-1200x1600.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528.jpeg%201320w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390897%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EA%20farmer%20harvests%20peanuts%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20carefully%20pulling%20the%20plants%20to%20collect%20the%20fresh%20crop%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20these%20hurdles%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20has%20witnessed%20remarkable%20growth%20in%20recent%20years.%20Revenue%20surged%20from%20Rs%2060%2C000%20in%202022%20to%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20in%202023%2C%20and%20is%20projected%20to%20reach%20Rs%2013-15%20lakh%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20transformation%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20collaboration%20and%20innovative%20solutions.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20getting%20better%20prices%20for%20each%20kilogram%20of%20peanuts%20we%20sell%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20see%20a%20real%20improvement%20in%20our%20seasonal%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aditya%20Sengar%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Unnao%2C%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20people%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20world%2C%20and%20studied%20these%20things%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20bring%20in%20fresh%20ideas%20to%20farming%2C%20learn%20about%20modern%20techniques%2C%20and%20open%20up%20new%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20expand%20their%20impact%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20is%20collaborating%20with%20the%20Chief%20Development%20Officer%20to%20map%20500%20hectares%20of%20land%20for%20a%20proposed%20peanut%20farming%20cluster.%20This%20initiative%20will%20not%20only%20provide%20farmers%20with%20recognition%20but%20also%20offer%20crucial%20support%20services.%20Once%20recognised%20as%20a%20cluster%2C%20farmers%20will%20gain%20better%20access%20to%20markets%2C%20strengthening%20their%20position%20and%20enabling%20them%20to%20achieve%20greater%20prosperity.%20Currently%2C%20the%20producer%20group%20comprises%2050%20farmers%2C%20but%20the%20ambitious%20cluster%20development%20plan%20aims%20to%20unite%202%2C000%20farmers%2C%20creating%20a%20powerful%20collective%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20issue%20we%20see%20around%20the%20world%20is%20that%20farmers%20aren%E2%80%99t%20getting%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352547%2Ffarmers-income-aneesh-jain-gram-unnati-value-chain-rajasthan-agri-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efair%20price%20for%20their%20produce%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20peanuts%20%E2%80%94%20whatever%20they%20grow%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20fair%20price.%20This%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20pain%20points%20we%E2%80%99ve%20observed.%20We%E2%80%99re%20not%20claiming%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20fixed%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20within%20our%20capacity%2C%20we%20are%20helping%20farmers%20mobilise%2C%20create%20clusters%2C%20and%20secure%20the%20incentives%20that%20are%20put%20in%20place%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sushant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20Image%20courtesy%20Aman%20Kumar%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734618600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.25-PM-1_11zon-1734